win-ldac
========
Copyright 2026 win-ldac contributors

This product includes software developed by the win-ldac contributors.

It bundles, links against, or references the following third-party
components. The original copyright notices and licence terms are
preserved here as required.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. libldac (Sony LDAC encoder)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Upstream:  https://android.googlesource.com/platform/external/libldac
Packaged:  https://github.com/EHfive/ldacBT (git submodule at vendor/ldacBT)
Licence:   Apache License, Version 2.0
Copyright (C) 2003 - 2016 Sony Corporation

Used to encode PCM into the LDAC bitstream that is sent over A2DP.
The encoder source is fetched via `git submodule update --init` and
compiled directly into the project — see CMakeLists.txt.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
